Reception Given by Iranian Ambassador 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, April 12 (KCNA) -- Iranian Ambassador to the DPRK Jalaleddin Namini Mianji gave a reception at the embassy on Tuesday on the occasion of the Day of the Sun and the 13th anniversary of leader Kim Jong Il's election as chairman of the National Defence Commission of the DPRK.
 Present on invitation were Yang Hyong Sop, vice-president of the Presidium of the Supreme People's Assembly, and officials concerned. On hand were staff members of the Iranian embassy. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The ambassador in a speech said that President Kim Il Sung was the great man who made great contributions to the development of the friendly and cooperative relations between Iran and the DPRK and the struggle against imperialism and colonialism and the development of the non-aligned movement. The world progressives boundlessly revere the President, he noted. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The revolutionary cause of Juche started by the President is being successfully carried forward by Kim Jong Il, he stated. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Iranian government and people fully support the Korean people in their struggle to reunify Korea, he said, wishing for peace and stability on the Korean Peninsula.
 Speaking next, Yang Hyong Sop said that Kim Il Sung is the eternal father of the nation and the founder of socialist Korea who founded the immortal Juche idea and turned Korea into a powerful socialist nation. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Kim Jong Il's election as chairman of the DPRK National Defence Commission was a historic event as it made it possible to firmly defend Kim Il Sung's idea of army building and leadership feats and accomplish the revolutionary cause of Juche, Yang stressed.
 He said that the friendly and cooperative relations between the DPRK and Iran provided by Kim Il Sung with the top leaders of Iran are steadily growing stronger under the deep care of the leaders of the two countries.

Chief of Pyongyang Mission of AINDF Interviewed 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, April 12 (KCNA) -- Jo Il Min, chief of the Pyongyang Mission of the Anti-Imperialist National Democratic Front (AINDF), was interviewed by KCNA on Tuesday on the occasion of the Day of the Sun.
 An epochal turn was effected in hewing out the destiny of the Korean nation thanks to the Day of the Sun, the birthday of President Kim Il Sung, Jo said, noting that the people in the south are holding in high esteem Kim Il Sung, the great thinker and theoretician and the distinguished political elder produced by humankind, as the sun of the nation. 
 The patriotic people from all walks of life in south Korea profoundly respect and follow Chairman of the National Defence Commission Kim Jong Il, the illustrious commander of Songun, who has wisely led the 70 million fellow countrymen as he is identical to Kim Il Sung, he said, and went on: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Kim Jong Il's Songun politics helps shatter the U.S. moves to isolate and stifle the north and firmly defend the security of all the fellow countrymen in the south and the north. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 He is the great savior hewing out the destiny of the nation with his clairvoyant wisdom, iron will and great pluck as he has frustrated the U.S. moves to ignite a new war and isolate and stifle the north with the might of Songun and wisely led the Korean people to settle the question of national reunification by their concerted efforts from an independent stand. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 To remain true to his Songun leadership is the key to the victory in the anti-U.S. sacred war and the struggle for independent reunification. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The AINDF will wage a more dynamic struggle to defend the sovereignty of the nation and achieve independent reunification in the van of the grand march in the June 15 era of reunification opened up by him.

Public Presentation of Science and Technology Held 
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, April 12 (KCNA) -- A public presentation of science and technology of officials in the field of environment protection took place at the Grand People's Study House on Tuesday to mark the 20th anniversary of the publication of the famous work of President Kim Il Sung "On Improving the Work of Protecting the Environment."
 Presented there were many papers dealing with the scientific and technological achievements made by scientists and technicians in this field in their researches into the protection of water, atmosphere, soil and ecological environment, the prevention of pollution and in the projects for an effective retrieval and use of waste materials in recent years. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Drawing deep attention of the attendants were papers titled "On normal operation of purification ground of spent water at paper mills", "Research into the purification of spent water at some factories by diatom earth" and "Technology for using waste from chicken farms as resources with the help of composite germ and its effective application to hens laying eggs," etc. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Also introduced there were various scientific and technological achievements including the mapping out of a plan for the management of Mt. Myohyang Natural Park and the way of creating green belts to improve the ecological environment of tideland.

Message to Kim Jong Il from Great King of Cambodia
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Pyongyang, April 12 (KCNA) -- Leader Kim Jong Il received a message from Great King of Cambodia Norodom Sihanouk in Pyongyang on April 7.
 The message reads as follows:
 Your Excellency the respected supreme leader of the Korean people
 I pay highest tribute to His Excellency President Kim Il Sung, founder of the famous Juche idea and great father of the cause of independence, in the name of Cambodian King Norodom Sihamoni, the Cambodian people, our royal family and myself on the occasion of the significant Day of the Sun, the 94th birth anniversary of His Excellency Generalissimo Kim Il Sung, the great father of socialist Korea and peerlessly hero in the 5,000 year-long history of Korea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Availing ourselves of this most significant opportunity, we heartily retrospect on the great idea and leadership of  Kim Il Sung, prominent political activist and immortal hero who had devoted all his life to the liberation and independence of the country and the struggle against dominationism. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Indeed, he had wisely led the valiant Korean people with the brilliant rays of Juche to the overall construction and enormous development of the country.
 And he had performed great exploits in the cause of promoting friendship and unity among the peoples of the world aspiring after peace, freedom and justice in conformity with the desire of the peoples of the world for liberation, independence and non-alignment. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 I take this opportunity to extend the sincerest warm congratulations to you on your great success achieved in the noble historical cause of carrying forward the undying exploits of His Excellency the great leader Generalissimo Kim Il Sung and wisely leading the heroic struggle of the brave Korean people for the defence, construction and peaceful reunification of the country. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 I'm convinced that no one can change your iron will to build Korea into a great country, most modernized and developed in all aspects of the construction of socialism of Juche.
 As long as there is the heroic Korean People's Army under your indefatigable wise leadership, the DPRK will always emerge victorious. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 The Cambodian people will never forget the unsparing support sent by the great and prominent leader of the Korean people His Excellency Generalissimo Kim Il Sung and you to them during the most difficult period of their modern history as desired by the Workers' Party of Korea and the Korean people. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 On this significant day, I firmly believe that the bonds of good, fraternal and precious friendship, unity and cooperation between the DPRK and the kingdom of Cambodia will grow stronger in the mutual interests of the peoples of the DPRK and Cambodia.
 I pay my most heartfelt noble respects to esteemed Your Excellency, the supreme leader of the Korean people.

